d"],"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"選擇產生的基金管道訂單，選擇‘初始化’狀態後，中點擊【數據發送】，彈框資訊確認無誤後，點擊【確認】，此時訂單狀況會變成'發送成功'","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"NJfZdDjL4ojY3YxEsPQj4bvSpGf"},{"block_id":"doxjpMt4NUtXIOUn5MXWk3h5Zwd","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1656,"token":"VjZWbMQ5LogD0Px3EeqjDJyDpxd","width":3278},"parent_id":"doxjpMdAkQ8dKMmkzMLCLwUngsg"},{"block_id":"doxjpczGuLJ3HLKVMkD0KBq3OFf","block_type":13,"children":["doxjpbcP6svim6iQXdP0zvvm0tc","doxjpmadVwivmjv63haQmkaEDgb"],"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"數據發送之後，选择“发送成功”的状态，等收到基金公司申購/贖回確認檔，這時在該基金記錄操作區，選擇「申购核对确认」、「赎回核对确认」，分别对「申购确认份额」和「赎回确认金额」进行填写和确认","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"NJfZdDjL4ojY3YxEsPQj4bvSpGf"},{"block_id":"doxjpbcP6svim6iQXdP0zvvm0tc","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1658,"token":"YQSibnizpogdczxbfl9jyrA4pLh","width":3304},"parent_id":"doxjpczGuLJ3HLKVMkD0KBq3OFf"},{"block_id":"doxjpmadVwivmjv63haQmkaEDgb","block_type":12,"bullet":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"核对确认的弹窗中，需要分别选择清算交收使用的「基金净值」，并分别填写「申购确认份额」和「赎回确认金额」","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"children":["doxjp10OZFow1c6zDx5nrnvJmvC"],"parent_id":"doxjpczGuLJ3HLKVMkD0KBq3OFf"},{"block_id":"doxjp10OZFow1c6zDx5nrnvJmvC","block_type":19,"callout":{"background_color":5,"border_color":5,"emoji_id":"gift","text_color":1},"children":["doxjp81PycdQf6kKWtIV8QTbwKh","doxjpyTaJRX44YXrsPwOiUqiHPe","doxjp6hs1nT7OdbW0xbIdq7NINh"],"parent_id":"doxjpmadVwivmjv63haQmkaEDgb"},{"block_id":"doxjp81PycdQf6kKWtIV8QTbwKh","block_type":2,"parent_id":"doxjp10OZFow1c6zDx5nrnvJmvC","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjpyTaJRX44YXrsPwOiUqiHPe","block_type":2,"parent_id":"doxjp10OZFow1c6zDx5nrnvJmvC","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"💡 1. 「申购核对确认」、「赎回核对确认」分开进行核对确认，同时申购交割和赎回交割流程也支持分开进行。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxjp6hs1nT7OdbW0xbIdq7NINh","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"如果所选「净值日期」无净值数据，需要前往净值表添加净值。申购份额和赎回金额的回填有自动校验机制，系统将根据申购提交金额、赎回提交份额和基金净值进行申购份额和赎回金额的计算，如果手动回填的数据与系统计算的数据差值在0.5时，点击『 确定 』将提示错误，需要重新填写。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"doxjp10OZFow1c6zDx5nrnvJmvC"},{"block_id":"doxjpd14C8Gf222cGXutKMIhPMh","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1678,"token":"PrBHbVojTo3Qcoxgb0RjgTa4pFd","width":1208},"parent_id":"NJfZdDjL4ojY3YxEsPQj4bvSpGf"},{"block_id":"doxjpEDIIIYMVTVaRjPUNBmff1d","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1646,"token":"XNo3bovZhoZ6MdxWIQrjf0e0pth","width":1174},"parent_id":"NJfZdDjL4ojY3YxEsPQj4bvSpGf"},{"block_id":"doxjpSTzePIMhy5lbZ2pA5fwHFc","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"若當天沒有訂單，自動核對確認， 自動完成交收。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false,"sequence":"auto"}},"parent_id":"NJfZdDjL4ojY3YxEsPQj4bvSpGf"},{"block_id":"doxjpKf3Sh63eErTRdtsVWVx9vg","block_type":13,"children":["doxjpcxjNWD5SHjXTcBb1TbI9nc"],"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"选择“交收中”的状态，選中對應管道單進行申購交割，點擊確認之後沒有問題申購就完成了","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false,"sequence":"auto"}},"parent_id":"NJfZdDjL4ojY3YxEsPQj4bvSpGf"},{"block_id":"doxjpcxjNWD5SHjXTcBb1TbI9nc","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1624,"token":"JXqMbpsWZoHEgFxzzg0jkGUmp1f","width":3280},"parent_id":"doxjpKf3Sh63eErTRdtsVWVx9vg"},{"block_id":"doxjpf0dzE6PK7y9sfHlQLkSpPd","block_type":13,"children":["doxjpdHZajYKGgishyjEhUipLQg","doxjp1ymiOgCnuVMfTilw7cDusc"],"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"後續如果申購交割完成之後還有贖回，會彈出來贖回貨交割，點擊完贖回或交割後是贖回錢交割，點完整個流程就結束了；如果沒有贖回，申購交割完成之後整個流程就結束了","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false,"sequence":"auto"}},"parent_id":"NJfZdDjL4ojY3YxEsPQj4bvSpGf"},{"block_id":"doxjpdHZajYKGgishyjEhUipLQg","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1648,"token":"HSxRb2q2yoRCmaxY7gFjFZp9pPh","width":3318},"parent_id":"doxjpf0dzE6PK7y9sfHlQLkSpPd"},{"block_id":"doxjp1ymiOgCnuVMfTilw7cDusc","block_type":27,"image":{"align":2,"height":1652,"token":"TUBQb1ibWo500Zxc75kjvrcEpHf","width":3304},"parent_id":"doxjpf0dzE6PK7y9sfHlQLkSpPd"}]}